"v.使对抗；与…对抗 【英】 v. 使对抗; 与…对抗(arouse hostility; show opposition ) 【考】 反义词：placate(安 抚); synergic(合作的); propitiate(劝解); mollify(平息) 【记】 ant(反)+agon(打斗， 比赛)+ize→对着打→ 对抗 【同】 派生词: antagonism (n.对抗，敌对opposi tion; enmity); antagonist (n. 敌手，对手); antagonistic (adj. 对抗的,敌对的) 【例】 It would be dangerous to antagonize him. v. 敌对; 与...对抗(arouse hostility; show opposition) 【记】ant = anti反对, 敌对, agon竞赛, 较量－对抗 【参】antagonism(n 对抗, 敌对) = opposition = enmity 【类】cowardice: intimidate = choler: antagonize懦弱因为被胁迫 = 愤怒因为被敌对 【反】placate(v 安抚); propitiate(v 劝解); mollify(v 平息) 【记】anti- 反 + go on 反着走，反着干 antagonize (v.)  1630s, ""to compete with,"" from Greek antagonizesthai ""to struggle against, oppose, be a rival"" (see antagonist). Meaning ""to struggle against continuously"" is recorded from 1742. Related: Antagonized; antagonizing."
